==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Constricted
<hw>Con*strict"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Drawn together;
bound; contracted; cramped.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Contracted or compressed so as to
be smaller in certain places or parts than in others.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>constricting</ent>⟦br⟧
